{"serial": "14007", "department_serial": 16, "code": "PD6309", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Modern Interpretation of Chinese Philosophy VII", "ch": "中國哲學現代詮釋VII"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Yang, Cho-Hon"], "ch": ["楊祖漢"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 3, "session": ["2", "3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "LS", "room": "301"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 15, "department": {"ch": "哲學研究所碩士班", "en": "Master of Philosophy"}, "system": {"ch": "碩博同修", "en": "Master/Doctoral Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 0, "selected": 13, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "當代新儒學的宋明理學研究成果豐富，深度表現了宋明儒學的哲學義理，活化成德之教的精神，對於當代華人的道德修養是不可或缺的參考。本課程通過當代儒學對宋明理學的詮釋，希望能比較有深度的展示宋明儒重要派別的主要思想，根據重要的宋明儒的文獻，給出當代的詮釋。", "en": "The research results of Neo-Confucianism in Song and Ming Dynasties are profound, which deeply shows the philosophical meaning of Confucianism in Song and Ming Dynasties and activates the spirit of moral education, which is an indispensable reference for the moral cultivation of contemporary Chinese. \nThrough the interpretation of Neo-Confucianism in Song and Ming Dynasties by contemporary Confucianism, this course hopes to show the main ideas of important schools of Song and Ming Confucianism in depth and give contemporary interpretations according to important documents of Song and Ming Confucianism."}, "outline": {"ch": "本課程擬對宋明理學的當代詮釋給出系統的敘述，也根據我最近的的研究心得，對程朱、陸王二系是否可以會通給出新的詮釋。對於此二系的會通，會引入康德的道德哲學的主要見解作為對照。對於重要的宋明理學的文獻，會選取《近思錄》與《傳習錄》中的文獻，來對程朱陸王之學作出比較。", "en": "This course gives a systematic description of the contemporary interpretation of Neo-Confucianism in the Song and Ming Dynasties, and also gives a new interpretation of whether Cheng Zhu and Lu Wang can communicate with each other according to my recent research experience. For the communication of these two systems, the main insights of Kant‘s moral philosophy will be introduced as a contrast. For the important text of Neo-Confucianism in Song and Ming Dynasties, we will choose the documents in “Jin Si Lu” and “Chuan Xi lu” to compare Cheng Zhu and Lu Wang’s philosophy."}, "textbook": {"ch": "楊祖漢、許惠敏編注：《近思錄》，香港中華書局。\n陳榮捷：《王陽明傳習錄詳註集評（修訂版七刷）》，台灣學生書局。\n楊祖漢：《楊祖漢新儒學論文精選集》，學生書局。", "en": "楊祖漢、許惠敏編注：《近思錄》，香港中華書局。\n陳榮捷：《王陽明傳習錄詳註集評（修訂版七刷）》，台灣學生書局。\n楊祖漢：《楊祖漢新儒學論文精選集》，學生書局。"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "50", "en": "50"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "課堂出席與討論 50％\n期末報告 50％", "en": "Attendance and Discussion 50％\nFinal Paper 50％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "週三下午", "en": "Wednesday PM"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "17+1", "en": "17+1"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "預留彈性時間", "en": "預留彈性時間"}, "domain": {"ch": "中國哲學現代詮釋課程群", "en": "中國哲學現代詮釋課程群"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "理論觀念", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "批判創造", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "研究教學", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "學理應用", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "人文素養", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "國際互動", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "ability to appreciate ideas and theories", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Research Report(printed on paper)", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "ability to think critically and creatively", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Research Report(printed on paper)", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "ability to undertake research and teaching", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Research Report(printed on paper)", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "ability to apply theory to real world", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Research Report(printed on paper)", "Attendanc